OL,3,C'Like a family break up' says former
OL,4,CPontins worker 'devastated' at closure
OL,6,F"It just closed. It was hard to
OL,7,Fbelieve at first because there were so
OL,8,Fmany people texting and on Facebook
OL,9,Fand on WhatsApp, you know, and
OL,10,Feverybody was in disbelief that it
OL,11,Fclosed down."
OL,13,FHe says it has had a huge impact on so
OL,14,Fmany people's lives with many worrying
OL,15,Fabout how they are going to cover
OL,16,Fbills and mortgage. "All of a sudden,
OL,17,Feverything's just cut from you", Mr
OL,18,FO'Neill said.
