OL,6,F"And the management was great as well.
OL,7,FWe got a really good team of managers,
OL,8,Fso everything was really good and
OL,9,Fthat's why I worked there.
OL,11,F"It's the longest job I've had in my
OL,12,Flife, so it must have been good."JSome
OL,13,Fof those who lost their job have now
OL,14,Ffound new employment at other holiday
OL,15,Fcamps in the area.
OL,17,FBut Mr O'Oneill says what is becoming
OL,18,Fan increasing source of concern is
OL,19,F"the company's silence on what they
OL,20,Fhave planned."
