OL,6,Fnd the Secretary of State for Media,
OL,7,FSport and Culture, Lucy Frazer MP has
OL,8,Fintervened, writing to the company
OL,9,Fsaying she has become concerned about
OL,10,Freports that the company is failing to
OL,11,Fengage and asking for a meeting.
OL,13,FLocal MP Dr James Davies says he wants
OL,14,Fto speak to the company to tell them
OL,15,Fof the interest there is in the site
OL,16,Ffrom tourism operators. He said: "I
OL,17,Fhave written to 14 companies with
OL,18,Ftourism backgrounds who are highly
OL,19,Fregarded. I've had responses from a
OL,20,Fgood number of those that are at least
OL,21,Fthree expressions of interest.
