OL,3,C'Like a family break up' says former
OL,4,CPontins worker 'devastated' at closure
OL,6,F"I'm aware of tourism-related
OL,7,Fcompanies interested in this site, in
OL,8,Fpurchasing this site, or taking it
OL,9,Fforward in a positive way. The
OL,10,Fdifficulty I'm having is making
OL,11,Fcontact with Britannia hotels.J"So the
OL,12,Flocal people, people who used to work
OL,13,Fhere, the residents living right next
OL,14,Fdoor, the whole town obviously want to
OL,15,Fknow the future of the site, why it
OL,16,Fshut? What Britannia hopes to do with
OL,17,Fit in the future."
