OL,6,FMr Davies continued: "I'm really keen
OL,7,Fto speak to Britannia because I want
OL,8,Fto express to them the interest I've
OL,9,Fhad from other companies in taking the
OL,10,Fsite on, but that is proving a real
OL,11,Fchallenge.J"Pontins in Southport and
OL,12,FCamba Sands have also shut, and I've
OL,13,Fbeen working with the MP from those
OL,14,Fareas and with the Secretary of State
OL,15,Ffor Culture, Media and Sport to
OL,16,Fexpress to her the concern that there
OL,17,Fis. And she has very helpfully written
OL,18,Fto Britannia to promote the importance
OL,19,Fof negotiation of discussion because
OL,20,Fthat's what we all want to see."
